<div class="modal-header">
  <h5 class="modal-title text-danger" id="verifyLabel">Couldn't Verify <%= character.name %></h5>
</div>
<div class="modal-body">
  <p>
    XIVAuth was unable to validate the verification code for <%= character.name %>. This likely means that the
    verification code was not placed on the relevant
    <%= link_to "Lodestone profile", character.lodestone_url, target: "_blank", rel: 'noreferrer noopener' %>, was not
    applied correctly, or Square Enix is taking too long to apply any requested changes.
  </p>
  <p>
    Verification may be retried by selecting the <strong>Verify</strong> button on the character's card. XIVAuth will
    not attempt to automatically re-verify this character.
  </p>
</div>
<div class="modal-footer">
  <div class="me-auto">
    <div class="text-secondary very-small align-middle">
      Job ID: <span class="font-monospace"><%= job.job_id %></span>
    </div>  </div>
  <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">Rats.</button>
</div>